      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been super well-loved? This beauty has been my trusty companion and is still running like a champ! It\u2019s in really solid shape and ready for all your upcoming road trips or daily commutes. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it\u2019s just waiting for a new home where it can keep making memories. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
