    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe, addressing critical chassis points. Suspension remains taut with upgraded bushings, while the ventilated rotors and multi-piston calipers provide consistent thermal management under load. Though it shows honest patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical synchronicity and throttle response remain razor-sharp.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Used sedan. Clean title. Regular maintenance performed. Interior intact. Minor exterior wear. Runs well.",
