    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 29500.0,
