      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L inline-six remains potent, featuring its signature individual throttle bodies and a recently serviced Double VANOS system for optimal cam timing. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement plates and upgraded bushings to mitigate common floor-pan fatigue, ensuring structural rigidity during high-lateral-G cornering. While displaying minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the performance envelope is well-preserved with a refreshed cooling system and preventative rod bearing replacement already completed. A true driver\u2019s specification optimized for turn-in precision and linear power delivery.",
